WEBVTT

00:00.166 --> 00:04.623
It was taken back in 2006, when
Grandma and Grandpa came to visit me

00:04.633 --> 00:06.123
and we all went out to brunch.

00:06.133 --> 00:07.994
We all look pretty
happy, right?

00:08.239 --> 00:09.299
Wrong.

00:09.309 --> 00:10.663
I wish your face
would melt off.

00:10.673 --> 00:11.943
I wish your eyeballs
would explode.

00:11.973 --> 00:14.417
- I hate you.
- I hate you more.

00:14.427 --> 00:16.621
- I'm going to kill him.
- I can't say I blame you.

00:16.631 --> 00:18.921
No, I mean I'm seriously
going to kill him.

00:18.936 --> 00:21.340
I don't care how unpleasant it is.
You have to talk to him.

00:21.352 --> 00:23.269
- Not now.
- Okay, if you don't, I will.

00:23.277 --> 00:24.483
Robin...

00:25.156 --> 00:27.843
Okay, for any of this to make sense,
you got to understand,

00:27.857 --> 00:29.710
there are three
parts to this story.

00:29.728 --> 00:32.150
Let's start with the
Marshall and Lily part.

00:34.036 --> 00:38.270
As a 30th anniversary gift, I had flown
my parents to New York for the weekend.

00:38.287 --> 00:40.371
Oh, I forgot to tell you,
your cousin Jimmy

00:40.385 --> 00:42.942
had a wonderful time at
that spa he visited.

00:42.958 --> 00:46.190
You mean the spa the judge ordered
him to go to to quit cocaine?

00:46.317 --> 00:47.710
Coffee?

00:48.015 --> 00:50.802
Now, Grandma and Grandpa didn't
like to talk about things

00:50.818 --> 00:52.863
that were
uncomfortable, emotional,

00:52.876 --> 00:54.872
or in any way... real.

00:54.886 --> 00:56.782
Hi, Mr. and Mrs. Mosby.

00:56.795 --> 00:58.792
Oh, Lily! Hi, Marshall.

00:58.808 --> 00:59.732
Good to see you.

00:59.746 --> 01:02.442
I was just stopping by to
pick up some of my things.

01:02.458 --> 01:05.753
Yes, we were so sorry
to hear about your...

01:05.778 --> 01:07.990
you know, the, the...

01:10.256 --> 01:11.251
Well...

01:11.266 --> 01:13.300
Lily calling off the
wedding and dumping me?

01:13.318 --> 01:16.333
Me begging Marshall to take
me back and him rejecting me?

01:16.346 --> 01:18.192
I love your hair.

